Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.18,0:02:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三話 死者不可復生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.33,0:03:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.61,0:03:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你老是這麼說 其實是很感謝我的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.03,0:03:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚可以陪我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.63,0:03:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.65,0:03:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 當我沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呂布奉先…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.35,0:04:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.19,0:04:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我與你的邂逅嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.06,0:04:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事？為什麼你會…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.03,0:04:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.47,0:04:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你」？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.11,0:04:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.63,0:04:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.30,0:04:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.59,0:04:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.20,0:05:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.25,0:05:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符姐姐 無需這麼著急
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.19,0:05:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是仲謀早起為我做的超美味便當啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.65,0:05:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在特等席上品嚐的話就太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您能這麼高興 我真是開心之極
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.72,0:05:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 以後可以每天都給我做嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.21,0:05:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 我會很開心地為您準備
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.27,0:05:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.38,0:05:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒這麼誇張吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.65,0:05:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是便當而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.96,0:05:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是媽媽嫌麻煩 叫我去超市自己買
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.25,0:05:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有人在議論我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.73,0:05:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是咖啡店裡哪一位呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.35,0:05:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過超市的店長也很帥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.77,0:05:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 仲謀要是按照今早的勢頭每天都做便當的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.28,0:05:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們家的經濟狀況就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我仲謀的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.13,0:06:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.11,0:06:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs25}別逃 你這烏鴉小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.89,0:06:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符姐姐 不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其擔心伯符 不如擔心烏鴉比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.01,0:06:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是一如既往地那麼熱鬧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.40,0:06:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樂就先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呂蒙小姐沒和您一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.43,0:06:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呂蒙今天沒有來上學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.81,0:06:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.68,0:06:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我有急事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.11,0:06:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？蒙蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.38,0:06:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之後 發生了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.05,0:06:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了呂布奉先你還能是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.38,0:06:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呂布奉先？那就是我的名字嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.77,0:06:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的什麼都記不得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.92,0:07:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連自己身為鬥士的事情也？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬥士？那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.65,0:07:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我一樣 擁有勾玉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.32,0:07:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那便是鬥士之證
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬥士之證…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那個時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.16,0:07:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢啊 左慈那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.42,0:07:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呂蒙 你的對手是老夫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.74,0:07:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醜話說在前面 少爺要比老夫我·士孫瑞強大十倍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:08:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 那個師範代真的要比左慈弱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.20,0:08:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 這宅邸真是宏大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.60,0:08:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左慈這傢伙 應該不會在自己的宅邸裡迷路吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.59,0:08:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.24,0:08:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫉妒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 你無需擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.05,0:08:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左慈君根本就沒把我放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.68,0:08:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.49,0:08:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他僅僅是為了打到我們洛陽君主·董卓 才會接近我而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.08,0:08:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙蒙還是小孩子 這種成年人間的關係是不會明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:08:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呂布 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 呂蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.00,0:09:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一事相求
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.23,0:09:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說這話的你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該已經死去了才對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天 你應該是去奔赴最後一戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.02,0:09:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 用盡了全部的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.57,0:09:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經死了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樂就？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.13,0:09:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼「什麼事」啊  我只是有些擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.52,0:10:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多餘的擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.19,0:10:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.23,0:10:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 呂蒙 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你聽得到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.91,0:10:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在 在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.61,0:10:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼在這種時候 你卻不在我身邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.11,0:10:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左慈…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說這話的你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.45,0:11:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該已經死去了才對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那現在待在這裡我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.48,0:11:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.17,0:11:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.64,0:11:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿呆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.93,0:11:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 阿呆烏鴉 你在小瞧我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.32,0:11:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿呆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.34,0:11:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又小瞧我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.23,0:11:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會再原諒你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.87,0:11:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿呆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.92,0:12:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.43,0:12:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我大忙了 這是很重要的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你餓了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.93,0:12:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.61,0:12:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.21,0:12:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然完全忘記了自己的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.17,0:12:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真有這種情況啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.01,0:12:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 有好多事情我也是馬上就記不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.72,0:12:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如別人的樣貌和姓名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全記不住 所以老是被公瑾教訓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.17,0:12:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.67,0:12:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是笨蛋 所以才會記不住嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.47,0:12:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你總是沉著臉 有點擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.84,0:13:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然人類在餓著肚子的時候是不會展現笑容的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必客氣 盡量吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.82,0:13:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.60,0:13:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.31,0:13:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃飽了 吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.26,0:13:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.81,0:13:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.50,0:13:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是公瑾和仲謀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.77,0:13:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跑到這裡來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.68,0:13:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼多的料理全部都吃掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.51,0:13:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符姐姐 我好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.20,0:13:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.15,0:13:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和她一起吃的 飯量剛剛好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.66,0:13:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.82,0:13:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是剛剛交的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.55,0:13:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.00,0:13:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 我還沒問你的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:13:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？怎麼了 公瑾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那制服 是洛陽的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你是 鬥士·呂布奉先？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.68,0:14:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她應該在與董卓的一戰之中丟掉了性命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.27,0:14:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.52,0:14:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然是鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.68,0:14:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說自己失憶了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.06,0:14:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了呂布奉先你還能是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.20,0:14:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似我的確是呂布奉先
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.49,0:14:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個本該死去的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.68,0:14:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孫子有言
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『亡國不可復存 死者不可復生』
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.83,0:14:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國家一旦滅亡即不可能再復原
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.38,0:14:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類一旦死亡即不可能再復生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.43,0:14:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 你卻在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你並未死去尚在人世的最佳佐證
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還尚在人世的佐證…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.79,0:15:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 你怎麼會死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.37,0:15:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布布
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.86,0:15:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.84,0:15:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪裡啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.04,0:15:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫院 讓華佗醫生看看她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.75,0:15:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼 怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.01,0:15:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs21}本日限定 全套餐半價
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs21}蜀漢套餐 30分鐘 100日元 盡情喝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs21}孫吳套餐 30分鐘 100日元 隨便吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs21}曹魏套餐 30分鐘 100日元 任你唱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.90,0:15:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天半價啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.88,0:15:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符 你在幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.88,0:15:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預定變更
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.44,0:15:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在去唱卡啦OK吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.14,0:15:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確現在去唱的話就趕不上下午課了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.18,0:15:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.71,0:15:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可是半價啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…可以比平時多唱2倍很幸運吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.64,0:15:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前 去醫院才是當務之急吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.37,0:15:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.65,0:15:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許唱卡啦OK會成為布布想起什麼的契機呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎？走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.54,0:16:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦？仲謀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公瑾哥哥 這裡是做什麼的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.51,0:16:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙 去哪裡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在找人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈媒師？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.15,0:16:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不巧 我不信神佛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.07,0:16:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更何況占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所要尋找的人 在東南方向距此地不遠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.08,0:16:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東南方向？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.67,0:16:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該可以聽到那個人的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.59,0:16:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會是在哪裡吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.74,0:17:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這裡唱卡啦OK啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.91,0:17:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲謀也唱點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.43,0:17:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對歌喉沒有什麼自信…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.83,0:17:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 和你姐姐正好相反呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.81,0:17:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以和公瑾哥哥同唱的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.40,0:17:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.56,0:17:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布布 有沒有你有印象的歌曲？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 我們兩個合唱一曲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看 這首如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那首歌是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.45,0:18:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這首很流行吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.99,0:18:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡這種啊 真意外
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布布？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.85,0:18:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.19,0:18:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.97,0:18:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的人是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.27,0:18:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有印象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.56,0:18:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 實際演唱一下的話或許就會記起更多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一事相求
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.87,0:19:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呂…呂布
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.82,0:19:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.89,0:19:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『天地·白狼擊』
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.22,0:19:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再變強一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.17,0:19:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的話 我是無法托付給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.06,0:19:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法托付？托付什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.78,0:19:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左慈君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.28,0:19:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.52,0:19:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經沒有時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.54,0:20:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了改變歷史的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.82,0:20:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 你就想以這幅身軀去奔赴戰場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.38,0:20:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.57,0:20:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬥士的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.82,0:20:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.68,0:20:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使不去反抗勾玉所指引的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.83,0:20:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是一路戰鬥至今的我 自己所選擇的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.41,0:20:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.64,0:20:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了自己 以自己的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.86,0:20:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的意志？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.15,0:20:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左慈君就拜託給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.28,0:20:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙蒙？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.22,0:21:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 蒙蒙和布布原來是這種關係啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.98,0:21:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呂布 一定是神將你的時間倒退回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.25,0:21:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…時間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.55,0:21:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠為了你自己 以自己的意志來使用的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.73,0:23:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天唱歌了 唱歌了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.44,0:23:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 公瑾和仲謀的合唱有種天生一對的感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.57,0:23:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯…伯符姐姐 您在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.54,0:23:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就…就是啊 伯符
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.98,0:23:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼我和仲謀般配…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.90,0:23:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？你們兩個怎麼了 幹嘛要對視？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.01,0:23:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？害羞了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.55,0:23:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可疑 總覺得很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.63,0:23:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四話 視卒如嬰兒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.63,0:23:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs25}出自《孫子兵法》：視卒如嬰兒 故可与之赴深溪  視卒如愛子 故可与之俱死
